menu "Emote"

    config APP_EMOTE_DEBUG_CONSOLE
        bool "On-device emote debug console"
        default y
        help
            Register the `emote` serial console command and the
            emote_debug_show/event/bat helpers used to review faces,
            state events (listen/speak/idle) and battery rendering
            directly on hardware. Intended for development builds;
            disable for release images to drop the debug surface.

endmenu
